title: Medical Marijuana Books and Magazines
description:
A small collection of books, articles, reports and magazines about Medical Marijuana for those who are suffering from cancer, AIDS/HIV and other diseases. 

Of course, today there is much more available out there on the internet than what is contained here. However, this provides a good starting point for those who are curious. Also, this contains the GAO report on MM published in November 2002 that the Bush Administration received with displeasure.


These files are compressed in a Rar archive to conserve bandwidth.
